title: Grateful Dead Live at Berkeley Community Theater on 1984-10-31
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Mama Tried-> Big River, Ramble On Rose, Minglewood Blues*-> Big Railroad Blues*, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Touch Of Grey, Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, I Need A Miracle*-> I Ain't Superstitous*-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Heaven Help The Fool Jam-> Morning Dew-> Around & Around*-> One More Saturday Night**, E: Satisfaction

*W/ Matt Kelly. ** One More Halloween Night

reviews.review_text: BCT '84 N4 (Halloween) High quality SBD, though not my favorite from the run and certainly not my favorite from this great month of '84. Shakedown and Dew highlights, to be sure. Space is neat, too, with the mind left bodyish jam. Otherwise, I can take or, really, leave this one.
